    {
      "source": "동아출판 프라임 영한사전",
      "matchType": "allterm:proximity:0.000000",
      "translatedText": "다시 한 번 말해 주시오",
      "text": "Excuse me? or Pardon me? or I <b>beg</b> your pardon. or What was that again? or Come again?"
